data.name: Dino Destruction
data.desc: Activate this Skill during your Main Phase. Once per turn, you can choose 1 Level 6 or higher Dinosaur monster you control. This turn, if it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage. Flip this card over at the end of the turn you activated this Skill.

card_sets.set_name: Speed Duel: Trials of the Kingdom
